l Horan\n|-\n| Best Pop\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"| [[iHeartRadio Music Awards]]\n| Best New Pop Artist\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"5\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.iheart.com/featured/iheartradio-music-awards/content/2018-01-09-2018-iheartradio-music-awards-see-the-full-list-of-nominee/|title=2018 iHeartRadio Music Awards: See The Full List of Nominee|publisher=[[iHeartRadio]]|date=10 January 2018|accessdate=12 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best New Artist\n| rowspan=2 {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Solo Breakout\n|-\n| Best Lyrics\n| \"Slow Hands\"\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Cover Song\n| \"[[Issues (Julia Michaels song)|Issues]]\"\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[BMI Awards|BMI Pop Awards]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Award Winning Songs\n|\"Slow Hands\"\n|rowspan=3 {{won}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bmi.com/news/entry/2018-bmi-pop-awards |title=Mark Ronson Receives the BMI Champion Award at the 66th BMI Pop Awards |date=8 May 2018 |work=BMI |accessdate=9 May 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|\"This Town\"\n|-\n| [[Society of Composers, Authors and Music Publishers of Canada|SOCAN]] Awards\n| Pop Music Awards\n|\"Slow Hands\"\n|<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.fyimusicnews.ca/articles/2018/06/19/29th-annual-socan-awards-honoured-canadas-best-class |title=29th Annual SOCAN Awards Honoured Canada's Best In Class |date=19 June 2018 |first=Kerry |last=Doole |work=Fyi Music News|accessdate=13 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[Teen Choice Awards]] \n| Choice Male Artist \n|rowspan=2|Niall Horan \n|rowspan=3 {{nominated}} \n|rowspan=\"3\"| <ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/awards/8469754/teen-choice-awards-winners-list-2018 |title=Teen Choice Awards Winners 2018: See the Full List (Updating Live) |date=12 August 2018 |first=Ashley |last=Iasimone |work=Billboard |accessdate=13 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Choice Summer Male Artist\n|-\n|Choice Summer Tour\n|[[Flicker World Tour]] \n|-\n|[[BMI Awards|BMI London Awards]]\n|Pop Award Songs\n|\"Slow Hands\"\n|{{won}}\n|